<para> The Multi-Tier ODBC Drivers for CA-Ingres consists of the generic ODBC client driver and the CA-Ingres Database agent on the server utilizing the built in database independent network layer for communication between the client and server.</para><para>The <ulink url="OpenLink">OpenLink</ulink>  Multi-Tier Drivers for CA-Ingres are a Type A class driver developed using the <ulink url="OpenAPI">OpenAPI</ulink>  call level interface.</para><para>These drivers are currently available for Ingres II versions 1.x, 2.x and beyond.</para><para>  [[/images/aodbcst.gif|]]</para><para> /Ingres Multi-Tier Architecture Diagram Image scaled down; Click to enlarge./</para><para> This driver is available for Windows, Linux, Unix(most flavours) Operating systems.</para><para> </para></section></docbook>